title: 365 days of self love
description: Bunny Williams worked for legendary decorators Sister Parish and Albert Hadley. Striking out on her own, she rose to the top rank of the interior design profession. Part memoir and part how-to manual, this work showcases many of the drop-dead chic but always costly comfortable residences whose interiors Williams has designed during her career.
Author: Williams, Bunny
